              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3235775073122376695">Rossant is a very interesting lady, with firm roots in the Middle East (Egypte, Lebanon) and the Western World (France, Spain, US). In these memoires she warmy describes her long stay in Cairo, with her grandparents, arond the second world war. As a culinary journalist she gives ample room to the local kitchen.<br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


